     FBATGR     UF A E           K DISK
     FCDBOAT    IF   E           K DISK
     FSYFA73FM  CF   E             WORKSTN
     F                                     SFILE(H50:ZRECNO)
     F                                     INFDS(FBAREA)
     D FBAREA          DS
     D  WSCLOC               370    371B 0
     D  WSSUBN               378    379B 0
